    "title": "Garrisoned Stronghold",
    "content": "Killzone: Volkus rule. When an operative wholly within a stronghold terrain feature is retaliating against an operative that isn't, the defender resolves first (this takes precedence over the normal fight resolution order).",
    "page_ref": null,
