    "title": "Breaching Charge",
    "content": "BREACHING CHARGE. Once per battle, when a friendly operative performs the Breach action, you can use this rule. If you do, that operative can perform that action for 1 less AP (to a minimum of 1AP) as though it had the word 'breach marker' on its datacard.",
    "page_ref": null,
    "version": null,
    "created_at": "2026-03-16 14:58:07",
