    "type": "equipment",
    "name": "MATRIX MANIPULATOR",
    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Once per battle, during a friendly CANOPTEK CIRCLE operative's activation or counteraction, you can use this rule. If you do, until the end of that activation/counteraction, a friendly CANOPTEK CIRCLE GEOMANCER operative is treated as your fourth OBELISK NODE marker.",
    "version": null,
