    "description": "Use this firefight ploy after rolling your attack dice for a friendly CELESTIAN INSIDIANT operative, if it's shooting against, fighting against or retaliating against an enemy operative that doesn't have the IMPERIUM keyword. That friendly operative's weapons have the Ceaseless weapon rule until the end of that sequence; if that enemy operative also has the CHAOS and/or PSYKER keyword, that friendly operative's weapons have the Relentless weapon rule until the end of that sequence instead.",
