    "description": "Whenever a friendly CORSAIR VOIDSCARRED operative is shooting with a shuriken rifle or ranger long rifle during an activation in which it hasn't performed the Charge, Fall Back or Reposition action, that weapon has the Accurate 1 weapon rule. Note that operative isn't restricted from performing those actions after shooting.",
