    "type": "tac_op",
    "name": "ROUT",
    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Archetype: SEEK-DESTROY\n\nREVEAL: The first time you score VP from this op.\n\nVICTORY POINTS: Whenever a friendly operative incapacitates an enemy operative, if that friendly operative is within 6\" of your opponent's drop zone, you score 1VP; if this is true and that enemy operative had a Wounds stat of 12 or more, you score 2VP instead. You cannot score more than 2VP from this op per turning point.",
