    "description": "Use this firefight ploy during a friendly FARSTALKER KINBAND operative's activation. Until the end of that activation, that operative doesn't have to control a marker to perform the Pick Up Marker or mission actions that usually require this (taking precedence over that action's conditions – it only needs to contest the marker).",
