    "cost": 1,
    "description": "Use this firefight ploy when you would counteract. You can do so with one friendly GOREMONGER operative that has a Conceal order, but you must change its order to Engage and it can only perform the Charge, Fight, or Shoot action during that counteraction.",
    "version": null,
