    "description": "Use this firefight ploy when a friendly GOREMONGER operative is incapacitated. Inflict damage determined by that friendly operative's GORE TANK on one enemy operative within that friendly operative's control range. Inflict:\n• D3 if empty.\n• D3+1 if half.\n• D3+2 if full.",
    "version": null,
