    "type": "equipment",
    "name": "BLOODY CADAVER",
    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Before the battle, you can set up one of your Bloody Cadaver markers wholly within your territory and more than 2\" from other markers (excluding your Gory Totem marker). Friendly GOREMONGER operatives can perform the Pick Up Marker action on that marker. In the Ready step of each Strategy phase, you can increase the GORE TANK of one friendly GOREMONGER operative that controls that marker, unless that friendly operative is within control range of an enemy operative.",
    "version": null,
