    "faction_id": 34,
    "type": "ploy",
    "name": "STALWART DEFENCE",
    "cost": 1,
    "description": "Use this Firefight Ploy when an enemy operative ends a move within the control range of a friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operative. Select one other friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operative visible to and within 6\" of that friendly operative, but that isn't itself within control range of enemy operatives. The selected operative can perform a free Shoot action. During that action:\n• It can target that enemy operative even though it's within control range of a friendly operative.\n• Other enemy operatives cannot be selected as a valid target.\n• Worsen the Hit stat of its weapons by 1.\n• You cannot select a frag or krak grenade, or a weapon with the Blast or x\" Devastating x weapon rule (e.g. Devastating 1\").",
    "version": null,
