    "type": "equipment",
    "name": "MAGNIFICATION CONDUITS",
    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Once per turning point, when a friendly APPRENTEK HIEROTEK CIRCLE or CRYPTEK HIEROTEK CIRCLE operative is performing the Shoot action, you can use this rule. If you do, select one other friendly HIEROTEK CIRCLE operative (excluding PLASMACYTE) that has an Engage order and is visible to that friendly operative. Until the end of that action, that other friendly operative can be treated as the active operative for the Magnify weapon rule.",
    "version": null,
