    "description": "Use this firefight ploy when a friendly KASRKIN operative performs the Fall Back action while visible to and within 6\" of another ready friendly KASRKIN operative that's not within control range of enemy operatives. After that friendly operative has finished moving, but before that Fall Back action ends, that other friendly operative can immediately perform a free Shoot action (you can change its order to Engage to do so).",
