    "type": "ploy",
    "name": "MALIGNANT AURA",
    "cost": 1,
    "description": "Use this firefight ploy when a friendly LEGIONARY NURGLE operative is performing the Shoot action, when you select a valid target.\n\nUntil the end of that action, whenever that operative is shooting an enemy operative within 3\" of it (i.e. including secondary targets, if any), its ranged weapons have the Piercing 1 weapon rule.",
    "version": null,
