    "faction_id": 62,
    "type": "equipment",
    "name": "PURITY SEALS",
    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Once per turning point, when a friendly PHOBOS STRIKE TEAM operative is shooting, fighting or retaliating, if you roll two or more fails, you can discard one of them to retain another as a normal success instead.",
