    "faction_id": 42,
    "type": "faction_rules",
    "name": "POISON",
    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Some weapons in this team's rules have the Poison weapon rule.\n\n*Poison: In the Resolve Attack Dice step, if you inflict damage with any successes, the operative this weapon is being used against (excluding friendly PLAGUE MARINE operatives) gains one of your Poison tokens (if it doesn't already have one). Whenever an operative that has one of your Poison tokens is activated, inflict 1 damage on it.",
    "version": null,
