    "type": "equipment",
    "name": "IMPERIAL CULT SYMBOL",
    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Once per turning point, when an operative is shooting a friendly SANCTIFIER operative that's benefitting from the SERMON, when you collect your defence dice, you can use this rule. If you do, change one of the attacker's retained critical successes to a normal success (any weapon rules they've already resolved aren't affected, e.g. Piercing Crits).",
    "version": null,
