    "description": "Whenever a friendly SCOUT SQUAD operative is shooting or fighting during its activation, if its order was changed from Conceal to Engage at the start of that activation, or it wasn't visible to enemy operatives at the start of that activation:\n• Its weapons have the Balanced weapon rule.\n• If the target is expended, its weapons have the Ceaseless weapon rule instead.",
    "version": null,
