    "description": "Up to twice per turning point, when a friendly SCOUT SQUAD operative is performing the Shoot action and you're selecting a valid target, you can use this rule. If you do, until the end of that action, its ranged weapons have the Lethal 5+ and Saturate weapon rules.",
