    "cost": 0,
    "description": "Whenever a friendly SCOUT SQUAD HEAVY GUNNER operative is shooting with a heavy bolter or missile launcher, if it hasn't moved during the activation, or if it's a counteraction, that weapon has the Ceaseless weapon rule; if the weapon already has that weapon rule, it has the Relentless weapon rule. Note that operative isn't restricted from moving after shooting.",
    "version": null,
    "subtype": null
