    "description": "Use this firefight ploy during a friendly TEMPESTUS AQUILON operative's activation (excluding SERVO-SENTRY and any operative with an APL stat greater than 2). During that activation it can perform the Pick Up Marker, Place Marker, or a mission action for 1 less AP.",
    "version": null,
