    "name": "NEUTRON OVERLOAD",
    "cost": 1,
    "description": "Use this firefight ploy when you resolve a critical success for a friendly VESPID STINGWING operative that is shooting with a neutron weapon during an activation in which it has moved or used FLY. If the target is within 4\" of it, inflict D3 additional damage.",
    "version": null,
