    "abilities_json": "[{\"name\":\"Soul Harvest\",\"description\":\"Whenever an enemy operative is incapacitated as a result of this operative's Part Collector rule or baleblade, you gain 1 Soul Harvest point, or two if that enemy operative had an APL stat of 3 or more. Whenever a friendly MANDRAKE operative is activated, you can spend 1 of your Soul Harvest points to either add 1 to its APL stat until the end of the battle, or have it regain 2D3 lost wounds. Note you can spend your Soul Harvest points even if this operative is incapacitated.\"},{\"name\":\"Part Collector\",\"description\":\"Whenever an enemy operative performs the Fall Back action while within control Range of this operative, you can use this rule. If you do, inflict 2D3 damage on that enemy operative before it moves.\"}]",
