    "abilities_json": "[{\"name\":\"*Poison\",\"description\":\"In the Resolve Attack Dice step, if you inflict damage with any critical successes, the operative this weapon is being used against gains one of your Poison tokens (if it doesn't already have one). Whenever an operative that has one of your Poison tokens is activated, inflict D3 damage on it.\"},{\"name\":\"TOXIC LUNGE (1AP)\",\"description\":\"Select one enemy operative within 2\\\" of this operative. Alternatively, if this operative is underground, select one enemy operative on your TUNNEL. Inflict D3+2 damage on that enemy operative and it gains one of your Poison tokens (if it doesn't already have one).\\n\\nThis operative can perform this action while underground (this takes precedence over the normal Burrow rules).\"}]",
